        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="callout-inner" style="margin-top: 18px;">
        <div>
          <p class="section-lede">Scotland chat: <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/E7JeZgcD9qFAyErBasRzmU" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">PauseAI Scotland WhatsApp</a></p>
